definition: abbr. for Uighur 維吾爾|维吾尔[Wei2 wu2 er3]/surname Wei
to preserve/to maintain/to hold together/dimension/vitamin (abbr. for 維生素|维生素[wei2 sheng1 su4])
to count/to count as/to regard as/to enumerate (sb's shortcomings)

sentences.english: In this dissertation, a new computation method of fractal dimension has been presented.
sentences.chinese: 本文提出了一种新的计算分形维数的方法。

sentences.english: Stably free dimensions of rings and modules are defined.
sentences.chinese: 引入了环和模的稳定自由维数。

sentences.english: So, the dimension constraints in 3D can be consilient with graphs in 2D.
sentences.chinese: 协同了尺寸三维约束与二维图形在维数上的不一致。

sentences.english: The dimension function of NTFW was characterized by showing its definition and properties.
sentences.chinese: 阐述了规范紧框架小波的维数函数的定义和相关性质。

sentences.english: Fractal dimensions of grains in the standard photographs are measured.
sentences.chinese: 测量了标准图谱中铁素体晶粒度图形的分形维数。

sentences.english: The paper also discuss the image's character by Box dimension.
sentences.chinese: 利用计盒维数讨论了图形的分形特征。

sentences.english: How to determinate those parameters of the time delay method were studied.
sentences.chinese: 并深入分析了延迟时间和相空间维数的确定原理。

sentences.english: The next example calculates the identity matrix for a given dimension.
sentences.chinese: 下面的例子是计算给定维数数组的单位矩阵。

sentences.english: Dimensionality reduction is an important preprocessing step before object recognition.
sentences.chinese: 维数约简是目标识别的一个重要预处理步骤。

sentences.english: In this paper, we introduce the concept of finitely cogenerated dimension of modules and study its properties.
sentences.chinese: 引入模的有限余生成维数的概念，研究了它的性质。

sentences.english: Retrieves the dimensions of the tightest bounding rectangle around the current clipping boundary.
sentences.chinese: 获取当前剪切边界周围最紧绑定矩形的维数。

sentences.english: The influences of pressure on the fractal dimension and the structure of micropore are discussed in details.
sentences.chinese: 详细讨论了分形维数和微孔结构随压力的变化规律。

sentences.english: There may be more dimensions as well.
sentences.chinese: 也可能存在更多的维数。

sentences.english: The search area of the FBD was reduced by the statistical method.
sentences.chinese: 然后，通过统计法缩小盒子维数的运算区域。

sentences.english: Feature selection and feature extraction are common methods for dimensionality reduction.
sentences.chinese: 特征选择和特征抽取是维数约简常用的两种方法。

sentences.english: The fractal dimensions of coke were calculated according to FHH model.
sentences.chinese: 根据FHH模型计算了焦炭的分形维数。

definition: (math.) an analytic function (of a complex variable)
